Author: yuvadeep
Title: [ANN] Fixy Network - Use of cryptocurrency in day to day life
Body: The Fixy Network fetches jointly for customers and retailers those who want to use cryptocurrency for the transactions. People who want to use the cryptocurrency have to buy a Fixy gift card that is available only in certified stores across the globe. New users who issued cards will be credited only when they have passed through the "Know your customer" and this process executes very fast and present users balance will be loaded directly into their wallets. Thus, the common plan of the Fixy marketplace is to connect users and the partners through a simple process. Retailers are those who want to sell the Gift Cards and the people who are in the group of the Fixy Networks. Fixy Token is used to pay for their membership and advertising fees. Fixy app will help all the companies and ICOs to reach to customers, they want to sell the brand goods more and get paid the money in both the cryptocurrency and fiat.
